By BO Staff Writer The following statement was previously published on the Black First Land First website: Black First Land First (BLF) is pleased to announce the following venue for the Special Policy Conference to be held on the 30 November 2019 in Durban (KZN): SEDA, 127 Johannes Nkosi Street (formerly Alice Street), Durban. Registration for attendance closes on the 10 November 2019. Should you wish to attend please send an email with your name, surname, telephone number and province to blackfirstlandfirst@gmail.com Those who have already made written requests to attend, kindly update your requests with all the required information. BLF further appeals for financial assistance towards hosting the conference. Your donations can be sent to the BLF Treasurer General under the following details: Name of account holder: Thandiswa Yaphi
